{
  "stem": "945.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But of course, we didn't know whether that was rumors, or whether that was true.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Later, of course, we found out, unfortunately, that not only was that true, but it was a lot worse than what we were told.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So that's how I lost my grandparents, and my youngest aunt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were gone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Our fate was not to be any different, as we soon found out, because like I said, on a given day, they told us all the Jewish people from Vyshnivets to gather up food to take along for 24 hours, and whatever belongings they could carry with them, and the rest was to stay behind.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was on a placard and pasted on the walls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was there for everybody to see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Again, we didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They told us that together at the station that we were going to go to another place, where there was going to be maybe work, or there was going to be-- they promised certain things.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the authorities kind of let it out, in a-- in a way, that the population should-- they deceived us, like they deceived everybody.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at that time, we tended to believe in something better.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We hoped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We hoped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You never gave up hope.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[WIPES NOSE] And so, on a nice fall day in October, I believe it was, 1941, the parade started.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Jewish people, with their [NON-ENGLISH], with their belongings, started marching towards the station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was about three mile, three kilometer walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The train station.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think I remember the Vyshnivets [NON-ENGLISH], his name was [NON-ENGLISH], ended up being a rabbi in Manchester after the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember him, because he was a very well-known personality in Vyshnivets.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
